The paper proposes a new indexing structure for parameterized strings, which is applicable for parameterized pattern matching problem. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the data structures (cs.DS) or discrete mathematics (cs.DM) sub-categories. The paper also discusses an online construction algorithm and the time complexity of finding all occurrences of a pattern in the text, which indicates that the paper may also belong to the computational complexity (cs.CC), information theory (cs.IT), or computational geometry (cs.CG) sub-categories.
